Reasoning: 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is the most likely category as the paper discusses recurrent neural networks and their application to time series prediction. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper compares different machine learning models for temporal signal processing. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper discusses the role of the reservoir as a dynamical system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also apply as the paper discusses the computational power and task-solving performance of different models. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses evaluation metrics for the models.
